sentences.english: The nearest hand belonged to Angela
Angelique cups her lips around Lenny's heel, and Lenny starts to moan.
sentences.chinese: 安吉麗用嘴罩住萊尼的腳後跟，萊尼呻吟起來。

sentences.english: Angelica is a practicing psychologist and modern life coach.
sentences.chinese: 安吉莉卡是職業心理醫生和時尚生活教練。

sentences.english: Angela was a fast subordinate of hers.
sentences.chinese: 安吉拉曾是她下屬中一個快嘴的人。

sentences.english: Angelica tells the story of a friendship that began in kindergarten.
sentences.chinese: 安吉里卡講述了一個從幼兒園開始的友誼故事。

sentences.english: My name is Angela and I was that witch which made you into the coma.
sentences.chinese: 我叫安吉拉，我就是那個讓你暈迷的女巫。

sentences.english: "I wore a hand-embroidered dress, " said the niece Angela, "for my wedding.
sentences.chinese: “我婚禮那天穿的是手工刺繡的禮服，”安吉拉說。

sentences.english: Lester asked the questions,and Angela kept getting them right.
sentences.chinese: 萊斯特提的問題，安吉拉回答各個正確。

sentences.english: Bacterial needle blight has became an epidemic of Chinese fir forests in Anji County in recent years.
sentences.chinese: 杉木細菌性葉枯病近幾年在安吉縣大量流行。

sentences.english: Sergio and Julia attend the wedding ceremony for Jeff and Angela.
sentences.chinese: 塞吉奧和朱莉婭參加了傑夫和安吉拉的結婚慶典。

sentences.english: To hold the distinguishing feature and make the sustainable development is the certain way for Anji to develop its bamboo tourism.
sentences.chinese: 抓住特色，持續發展是安吉竹旅遊發展的必由之路。

sentences.english: Andrea, the first named storm of the year is spinning off the coast.
sentences.chinese: 安吉爾，這一年第一個被命名的風暴正在海岸邊盤旋。

sentences.english: Getting into the back seat, Angelique hands you a business card.
sentences.chinese: 坐上後座，安吉麗遞給你一張名片。

sentences.english: It also has China's largest bamboo nursery.
sentences.chinese: 安吉縣同時也是中國最大的竹苗圃。
